I anticipate that Samantha will be out of the office for a time.  In order

that Samantha's work in progress be covered in her absence, please take the

following steps.  The attorneys should retrieve from her desk and files those

current file matters for which they are responsible.  To the extent you and

your administrative assistant can cover the file matters, please do so in

order to maintain a reasonable workload for the other paralegals.  If some of

your file matters need further paralegal assistance, please advise me so that

reassignments to other paralegals can be coordinated based upon the workloads

of Susan, Stephanie, and Tana.  Thank you.


